(66, 3, 2005, 2, 2, 14, '1327530463.jpg', 'Following the break out, Tony Stark and Steve Rogers are discussing the events that occurred.  Steve retells the events, trying to get Tony to reconsider it from a different view point.<br /><br /><br />\r\n<br /><br /><br />\r\nThe Purple Man was unable to control Luke Cage due to the drugs he was being fed in his food.  Luke proceeds to beat him to a pulp.  Steve manages to talk him down from killing him.<br /><br /><br />\r\n<br /><br /><br />\r\nSteve uses the image of all the heroes thrown into a situation and working together to remind Tony of how the original Avengers started, and that this was a sign for them to start a new Avengers.<br /><br /><br />\r\n<br /><br /><br />\r\nTony is reluctant, but Steve takes that as support and proceeds to approach Peter Parker, Luke Cage, Jessica Drew and Daredevil.<br /><br /><br />\r\n<br /><br /><br />\r\nOnly DareDevil declines because he doesn''t want the Avengers and Steve tarnished with the dirt that he has been hit with in the tabloids.<br /><br /><br />\r\n<br /><br /><br />\r\nThey all meet in a building donated by Tony to the New Avengers.<br /><br /><br />\r\n<br /><br /><br />\r\nJessica is seen agreeing to spy on SHIELD and the New Avengers with an unseen person.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 737699300, '{"1327530463":{"comic":"14","issue_number":"3","year_published":"2005","month_published":"2","day_published":"2","image":"1327530463.jpg","comic_summary":"Following the break out, Tony Stark and Steve Rogers are discussing the events that occurred.  Steve retells the events, trying to get Tony to reconsider it from a different view point.\\r\\n\\r\\nThe Purple Man was unable to control Luke Cage due to the drugs he was being fed in his food.  Luke proceeds to beat him to a pulp.  Steve manages to talk him down from killing him.\\r\\n\\r\\nSteve uses the image of all the heroes thrown into a situation and working together to remind Tony of how the original Avengers started, and that this was a sign for them to start a new Avengers.\\r\\n\\r\\nTony is reluctant, but Steve takes that as support and proceeds to approach Peter Parker, Luke Cage, Jessica Drew and Daredevil.\\r\\n\\r\\nOnly DareDevil declines because he doesn''t want the Avengers and Steve tarnished with the dirt that he has been hit with in the tabloids.\\r\\n\\r\\nThey all meet in a building donated by Tony to the New Avengers.\\r\\n\\r\\nJessica is seen agreeing to spy on SHIELD and the New Avengers with an unseen person.","arc_events":false,"characters":["51"],"character_events":[""],"arc_id":false,"previous_event_id":false,"next_event_id":false}}', 0, '', 'published', '2012-06-16 13:00:00'),
(67, 4, 2005, 3, 1, 14, '1327530604.jpg', 'On the arrival of Jessica Drew to the first meeting of the New Avengers, Tony contacts Maria Hill, acting director of S.H.I.E.L.D.  She immediately expresses her disapproval of a ''New Avengers'', but Steve points out that his ''Full Champion License'' entitles him to assemble any team he sees fit.<br /><br />\r\n<br /><br />\r\nSteve eventually gets the access and cooperation despite Hill''s misgivings.<br /><br />\r\n<br /><br />\r\nSpiderman is able to identify Electro as the instigator and facilitator of the breakout on The Raft.  The team then heads off to Boston to track him down.<br /><br />\r\n<br /><br />\r\nElectro is trying to convince his girlfriend to runaway with him when The New Avengers arrive.  He is quickly contained but faints when Luke Cage threatens to beat on him.<br /><br />\r\n<br /><br />\r\nJessica decides to take a different approach and bribes the remaining Raft prisoners with baked goods, she is quickly offered the name Kyle Lycos.  Although the file on Lycos is locked, Spiderman is able to brief them on what he knows about Kyle Lycos, A.K.A Sauron.<br /><br />\r\n<br /><br />\r\nJessica discovers that the S.H.I.E.L.D outpost outside the Savage Land is offline so they head off to investigate.<br /><br />\r\n<br /><br />\r\nDespite managing to land safely (much to Spiderman''s amazement) they are immediately attacked by a dinosaur.  They split up but Jessica and Luke encounter Wolverine who has his claws at Jessica''s throat.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 737699300, '{"1327530604":{"comic":"14","issue_number":"4","year_published":"2005","month_published":"3","day_published":"1","image":"1327530604.jpg","comic_summary":"On the arrival of Jessica Drew to the first meeting of the New Avengers, Tony contacts Maria Hill, acting director of S.H.I.E.L.D.  She immediately expresses her disapproval of a ''New Avengers'', but Steve points out that his ''Full Champion License'' entitles him to assemble any team he se