(87, 23, 2006, 2, 22, 13, '1331063057.jpg', 'Eight weeks prior to M-Day:<br /><br /><br />\r\n<br /><br /><br />\r\nStryker and his Purifiers are searching through a database until Stryker comes across the name Julia Cabot.  Stryker then confronts Jay Guthrie in the church whilst he is praying and tells him that Julia is waiting for him and that God sent an angel to be with her when she died and that he was the angel, Stryker reveals Jay''s wings.<br /><br /><br />\r\n<br /><br /><br />\r\nPresent Day:<br /><br /><br />\r\n<br /><br /><br />\r\nThe previous issues forward flashes catch up with the present as Jay Guthrie is discovered by Scott and Emma on the Mansion doorstep with his wings amputated.<br /><br /><br />\r\n<br /><br /><br />\r\nElixir is keeping Wallflower company whilst she sleeps in the infirmary and is woken by their arrival.  He wants to help but his presence makes Jay hysterical.  Emma sends him away after making him forget what he saw.<br /><br /><br />\r\n<br /><br /><br />\r\nEmma assembles all the mutant students in the Danger Room and pits the students against each other in a battle, the winners are offered a chance to train as X-Men.<br /><br /><br />\r\n<br /><br /><br />\r\nEmma orders Hellion to take out X-23 first. X-23 does well whilst Hellion deals with Rockslide and Surge but Emma uses her powers to interfere and prevent X-23 from moving.<br /><br /><br />\r\n<br /><br /><br />\r\nEmma singles out Mercury, Dust, Hellion, Elixir, Rockslide and Surge to train as X-Men.  Scott who just arrives adds X-23 to the roster.  Emma assigns Surge as the team leader to the surprise of both Surge and Hellion.<br /><br /><br />\r\n<br /><br /><br />\r\nWhilst Emma gives an assembly telling the remaining mutants that they are a dieing species, Stryker addresses thousands telling them that mutants are seeds of the devil.<br /><br /><br />\r\n<br /><br /><br />\r\nThe de-powered students are smuggled out of the mansion through the Morlock tunnels to a waiting bus to take them away from the Mansion, but as they drive off a missile is fired hitting the bus and the children inside.', 5, NULL, NULL, 100002077828287, '{"1331063057_100002077828287":{"comic":"13","issue_number":"23","year_published":"2006","month_published":"2","day_published":"22","image":"1331063057.jpg","comic_summary":"Eight weeks prior to M-Day:\\r\\n\\r\\nStryker and his Purifiers are searching through a database until Stryker comes across the name Julia Cabot.  Stryker then confronts Jay Guthrie in the church whilst he is praying and tells him that Julia is waiting for him and that God sent an angel to be with her when she died and that he was the angel, Stryker reveals Jay''s wings.\\r\\n\\r\\nPresent Day:\\r\\n\\r\\nThe previous issues forward flashes catch up with the present as Jay Guthrie is discovered by Scott and Emma on the Mansion doorstep with his wings amputated.\\r\\n\\r\\nElixir is keeping Wallflower company whilst she sleeps in the infirmary and is woken by their arrival.  He wants to help but his presence makes Jay hysterical.  Emma sends him away after making him forget what he saw.\\r\\n\\r\\nEmma assembles all the mutant students in the Danger Room and pits the students against each other in a battle, the winners are offered a chance to train as X-Men.\\r\\n\\r\\nEmma orders Hellion to take out X-23 first. X-23 does well whilst Hellion deals with Rockslide and Surge but Emma uses her powers to interfere and prevent X-23 from moving.\\r\\n\\r\\nEmma singles out Mercury, Dust, Hellion, Elixir, Rockslide and Surge to train as X-Men.  Scott who just arrives adds X-23 to the roster.  Emma assigns Surge as the team leader to the surprise of both Surge and Hellion.\\r\\n\\r\\nWhilst Emma gives an assembly telling the remaining mutants that they are a dieing species, Stryker addresses thousands telling them that mutants are seeds of the devil.\\r\\n\\r\\nThe de-powered students are smuggled out of the mansion through the Morlock tunnels to a waiting bus to take them away from the Mansion, but as they drive off a missile is fired hitting the bus and the children inside.","arc_events":false,"characters":["51"],"character_events":[""],"arc_id":"5","previous_event_id":false,"next_event_id":false}}', 0, '', 'published', '2012-06-16 13:00:00');
