(91, 25, 2006, 4, 12, 13, '1331838647.jpg', 'Whilst the New X-Men are training with Emma Frost and Colossus, Matthew Risman a Purifier working for Stryker takes up a sniper position.  An implant keeps him invisible from Sentinels and telepaths.<br /><br /><br />\r\n<br /><br /><br />\r\nThe New X-Men suffer a humiliating defeat by Colossus causing Elixir to lose his temper and strike him when the test is over and he has reverted to his flesh state.<br /><br /><br />\r\n<br /><br /><br />\r\nEmma kicks him from the team.<br /><br /><br />\r\n<br /><br /><br />\r\nLaurie approaches Sam Guthrie about Elixir as she is worried he is not coping with the loss of all their friends.   Sam advises she tells him how she feels.<br /><br /><br />\r\n<br /><br /><br />\r\nJay approaches Sooraya and asks her to tell Sam and Paige he loves them if he doesn''t come back.  He slips her an address but Laura tells her not to trust him as he smells of death.<br /><br /><br />\r\n<br /><br /><br />\r\nWhilst Laurie tries to talk to Elixir Matt Risman assassinates Laurie with a sniper rifle as Elixir can do nothing but watch.<br /><br /><br />\r\n<br /><br /><br />\r\nAs Risman reports his mission success Jay approaches Stryker''s church, he confronts the Stryker as he promised to help save his friends, Stryker shows him the source of his visions: Nimrod.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 100002077828287, '{"1331838647_100002077828287":{"comic":"13","issue_number":"25","year_published":"2006","month_published":"4","day_published":"12","image":"1331838647.jpg","comic_summary":"Whilst the New X-Men are training with Emma Frost and Colossus, Matthew Risman a Purifier working for Stryker takes up a sniper position.  An implant keeps him invisible from Sentinels and telepaths.\\r\\n\\r\\nThe New X-Men suffer a humiliating defeat by Colossus causing Elixir to lose his temper and strike him when the test is over and he has reverted to his flesh state.\\r\\n\\r\\nEmma kicks him from the team.\\r\\n\\r\\nLaurie