(97, 4, 2004, 8, 25, 8, '1332110556.jpg', 'Ord reminisces about the events in his life that brought him to this point, he comes from a violent society and he longs to return to his natural ways.<br /><br /><br />\r\n<br /><br /><br />\r\nThe X-Men prepare to break into Benetech to find the body they are testing on.<br /><br /><br />\r\n<br /><br /><br />\r\nBack at the mansion Ord has entered the Mansion and comes across Hisako and Wing.  He seems very disappointed to discover the X-Men are not present and eventually attacks the duo causing Hisako to activate her power an defend Wing.<br /><br /><br />\r\n<br /><br /><br />\r\nOrd manages to fend off Wing and attacks Wing, injecting him with something.<br /><br /><br />\r\n<br /><br /><br />\r\nHe tells Wing to the X-Men a message, that ''the mutant abomination will never be a threat to the Breakworld.''  He drops Wing from a great height.<br /><br /><br />\r\n<br /><br /><br />\r\nThe X-Men find a dead female mutant, but they don''t recognize her.  Emma receives a distress message from the Stepford Cuckoos, she tells them they need to return to the mansion but they attacked by men with non-lethal weapons.<br /><br /><br />\r\n<br /><br /><br />\r\nKitty has phased through a solid metal floor that is very deep, at least a hundred feet.  The metal felt extra-terrestrial.  She finds a vault door and picks the lock but the guards shoot at her and she phases.  The bullets hit a metallic being on the inside of the vault and he exits: Colossus.<br /><br /><br />\r\n<br /><br /><br />\r\nColossus takes out the guards before Kitty can talk him down, but he breaks down when he sees her, hoping he is finally, truly, dead.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 100002077828287, '{"1332110556_100002077828287":{"comic":"8","issue_number":"4","year_published":"2004","month_published":"8","day_published":"25","image":"1332110556.jpg","comic_summary":"Ord reminisces about the events in his life that brought him to this point, he comes from a violent 