(104, 5, 2004, 9, 22, 8, '1370112337.jpg', '<p>As Cyclops lays on the floor bleeding out and hallucinating, Emma pleads with the guards to get help but they refuse.<br /><br /> <br /><br /> <br /><br /> <br /><br /> Meanwhile, Elixir heals Wing but when he awakens he realises his powers are gone.<br /><br /> <br /><br /> <br /><br /> <br /><br /> Whilst Kitty recovers her strength for the return trip to the surface she tries to deal with the fact that Piotr Rasputin(Colossus) might still be alive.<br /><br /> <br /><br /> <br /><br /> <br /><br /> Kavita Rao arrives to find the X-Men under guard and Cyclops bleeding. Whilst Beast berates the Doctor, Emma coordinates with the X-Men and they disable the guards.<br /><br /> <br /><br /> As they are about to leave Ord bursts through the wall after returning from the X-Mansion. As they are about to fight Kitty arrives with Colossus rendering the X-Men speechless and catching Ord off-guard.<br /><br /> <br /><br /> As Colossus defeats Ord Nick Fury arrives with SHIELD and holds them all at gunpoint.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, 737699300, 'Array', 0, '', 'published', '2012-06-16 13:07:00'),
(105, 6, 2004, 11, 3, 8, '1336737622.jpg', 'GIFTED: 6/6<br /><br /><br />\r\n<br /><br /><br />\r\nIn a flashback we see Ord giving Dr. Rao information for a ''cure'' for being a mutant and that Ord was working with Abigail Brand of SWORD.<br /><br /><br />\r\n<br /><br /><br />\r\nIn the present the X-Men are furious to learn that Ord ha diplomatic immunity and is untouchable.<br /><br /><br />\r\n<br /><br /><br />\r\nFury orders them to walk away but they refuse.<br /><br /><br />\r\n<br /><br /><br />\r\nFury questions Colossus'' return but Emma, Hank and Logan confirm it''s him.<br /><br /><br />\r\n<br /><br /><br />\r\nFury states that he didn''t know Ord was torturing and testing Colossus but orders Brand to explain her position to the X-Men.  It turns out that where SHIELD handles matters on Earth, SWORD deals with threats from space.<br /><br /><br />\r\n<br /><br /><br />\r\nAs they are talking, desperate mutants break in wanting the cure.  During the commotion Ord escapes.  Kitty drags Brand away from the fight where the X-Men make her finish her story.<br /><br /><br />\r\n<br /><br /><br />\r\nOrd''s homeworld, The Breakworld, has the ability to see glimpses of the future, they saw that a mutant, likely an X-Man would destroy the entire planet.<br /><br /><br />\r\n<br /><br /><br />\r\nBrand states that Fury didn''t know what was happening to Colossus but Hank wants to know if Dr. Rao knew.<br /><br /><br />\r\n<br /><br /><br />\r\nRao bursts in begging for help as Ord has kidnapped the little girl, Tildie.<br /><br /><br />\r\n<br /><br /><br />\r\nOrd begins his escape on a spaceship with the girl, the cure and all the information.  Colossus and Wolverine join up again as Colossus hurls Wolverine at the fleeing ship.<br /><br /><br />\r\n<br /><br /><br />\r\nLogan forces Ord to land safely saving the girl and the cure.  But SHIELD takes Ord into custody and declares that everyone is going to walk away and say that nothing happened.<br /><br /><br />\r\n<br /><br /><br />\r\nThe X-Men return home with the knowledge that a war is looming and Ord is the Vanguard.  Hank and Scott discuss the cure and how it will soon be in the hands of governments.<br /><br /><br />\r\n<br /><br /><br />\r\nAs Emma watches Kitty and Piotr reconnect someone talks to her and they decide that she must be dealt with first... but not why or how.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 100002077828287, '{"1336737622_":{"comic":"8","issue_number":"6","year_published":"2004","month_published":"11","day_published":"3","image":"1336737622.jpg","comic_summary":"GIFTED: 6\\/6\\r\\n\\r\\nIn a flashback we see Ord giving Dr. Rao information for a ''cure'' for being a mutant and that Ord was working with Abigail Brand of SWORD.\\r\\n\\r\\nIn the present the X-Men are furious to learn that Ord ha diplomatic immunity and is untouchable.\\r\\n\\r\\nFury orders them to walk away but they refuse.\\r\\n\\r\\nFury questions Colossus'' return but Emma, Hank and Logan confirm it''s him.\\r\\n\\r\\nFury states that he didn''t know Ord was torturing and testing Colossus but orders Brand to explain her position to the X-Men.  It turns out that where SHIELD handles matters on Earth, SWORD deals with threats from space.\\r\\n\\r\\nAs they are talking, desperate mutants break in wanting the cure.  During the commotion Ord escapes.  Kitty drags Brand away from the fight where the X-Men make her finish her story.\\r\\n\\r\\nOrd''s homeworld, The Breakworld, has the ability to see glimpses of the future, they saw that a mutant, likely an X-Man would destroy the entire planet.\\r\\n\\r\\nBrand states that Fury didn''t know what was happening to Colossus but Hank wants to know if Dr. Rao knew.\\r\\n\\r\\nRao bursts in begging for help as Ord has kidnapped the little girl, Tildie.\\r\\n\\r\\nOrd begins his escape on a spaceship with the girl, the cure and all the information.  Colossus and Wolverine join up again as Colossus hurls Wolverine at the fleeing ship.\\r\\n\\r\\nLogan forces Ord to land safely saving the girl and the cure.  But SHIELD takes Ord into custody and declares that everyone is going to walk away and say that nothing happened.\\r\\n\\r\\nThe X-Men return home with the knowledge that a war is looming and Ord is the Vanguard.  Hank and Scott discuss the cure and how it will soon be in the hands of governments.\\r\\n\\r\\nAs Emma watches Kitty and Piotr reconnect someone talks to her and they decide that she must be dealt with first... but not why or how.","characters":["35"],"character_events":["Hank is very insistent that Brand tells him if Kavita Rao knew what was happening to Piotr, no reason is given but it seems very important to him.\\r\\n\\r\\nHe still has a sample of the cure but he tells Scott he doesn''t intend to use it yet.  An X-Man doesn''t quit."],"arc_id":false,"previous_event_id":false,"next_event_id":false}}', 0, '', 'published', '2012-06-16 13:08:00');
