(107, 7, 2004, 12, 22, 8, '1336759606.jpg', 'Danger: 1/6<br /><br /><br />\r\n<br /><br /><br />\r\nWing wanders through trees and grass denying to himself that he is now powerless.<br /><br /><br />\r\n<br /><br /><br />\r\nThe X-Men fight a multi-storey tall green monster during which each one has their own thoughts to contend with as the battle.  The Fantastic Four arrive and Ben is not pleased that they are on their turf.<br /><br /><br />\r\n<br /><br /><br />\r\nMeanwhile Wing appears to talk with Hisako who seems to encourage him to jump off the cliff he is standing on.<br /><br /><br />\r\n<br /><br /><br />\r\nThe combined forces of the X-Men and the Fantastic Four eventually subdue the monster.  Whilst talking with Reed and Sue it is brought up that the X-Men fighting alongside the Fantastic Four will bring good publicity for mutants, Scott doesn''t deny that this was his plan.<br /><br /><br />\r\n<br /><br /><br />\r\nAbigail Brand is brought before a tribunal to answer for her actions regarding Ord.  She remains defiant that she wouldn''t do anything different and that she wouldn''t change what she will do.  She claims an X-Man will destroy the Breakworld.<br /><br /><br />\r\n<br /><br /><br />\r\nThe X-Men are disappointed that their battle didn''t make the news.  They are interrupted by Hisako bursting in and looking for help for Wing as he is missing.<br /><br /><br />\r\n<br /><br /><br />\r\nBlindfold and the Stepford Cuckoos are able to sense him but Emma is not.<br /><br /><br />\r\n<br /><br /><br />\r\nWing lies dead at the bottom of the cliff... which is revealed to actually be the Danger Room.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 100002077828287, '{"1336759606_":{"comic":"8","issue_number":"7","year_published":"2004","month_published":"12","day_published":"22","image":"1336759606.jpg","comic_summary":"Danger: 1\\/6\\r\\n\\r\\nWing wanders through trees and grass denying to himself that he is now powerless.\\r\\n\\r\\nThe X-Men fight a multi-storey tall green monster during which each one has their own thoughts to contend with as the battle.  The Fantastic Four arrive and Ben is not pleased that they are on their turf.\\r\\n\\r\\nMeanwhile Wing appears to talk with Hisako who seems to encourage him to jump off the cliff he is standing on.\\r\\n\\r\\nThe combined forces of the X-Men and the Fantastic Four eventually subdue the monster.  Whilst talking with Reed and Sue it is brought up that the X-Men fighting alongside the Fantastic Four will bring good publicity for mutants, Scott doesn''t deny that this was his plan.\\r\\n\\r\\nAbigail Brand is brought before a tribunal to answer for her actions regarding Ord.  She remains defiant that she wouldn''t do anything different and that she wouldn''t change what she will do.  She claims an X-Man will destroy the Breakworld.\\r\\n\\r\\nThe X-Men are disappointed that their battle didn''t make the news.  They are interrupted by Hisako bursting in and looking for help for Wing as he is missing.\\r\\n\\r\\nBlindfold and the Stepford Cuckoos are able to sense him but Emma is not.\\r\\n\\r\\nWing lies dead at the bottom of the cliff... which is revealed to actually be the Danger Room.","characters":["51"],"character_events":[""],"arc_id":false,"previous_event_id":false,"next_event_id":false}}', 0, '', 'published', '2012-06-16 13:09:00'),
(120, 8, 2005, 2, 16, 8, '1370112666.jpg', '<p>As the X-Men are about to begin their search for Wing, Emma Frost and all the other telepaths are struck with severe pain before being rendered unconscious.<br /><br /> <br /><br /> <br /><br /> <br /><br /> Elsewhere two men watch as a badly damaged Sentinel they salvaged comes to life and starts moving away.<br /><br /> <br /><br /> <br /><br /> <br /><br /> Wolverine is unable to detect any form of attack that would cause the telepaths to collapse and Wing to vanish. <br /><br /> <br /><br /> <br /><br /> <br /><br /> As Scott tries to revive Emma she hears a voice taunting her and her relationship with Scott, but she doesn&rsquo;t awaken.<br /><br /> <br /><br /> <br /><br /> <br /><br /> Agent Brand receives word that all their taps and surveillance within the mansion are now offline but they don&rsquo;t know if they have been discovered by the X-Men.<br /><br /> <br /><br /> <br /><br /> <br /><br /> As the X-Men realise that they have been cut off from the outside world in everyway short of physically leaving the area Lockheed arrives and warns them that something is coming.<br /><br /> <br /><br /> <br /><br /> <br /><br /> They rush outside to find the damaged Sentinel. Whilst the X-Men engage the deranged machine, which rambles on about &lsquo;oppressors&rsquo; and it&rsquo;s &lsquo;Lord&rsquo;, Kitty moves the kids to the Danger Room for safety. Scott, wanting the battle ended quickly, removes his visor and unleashes a powerful blast that sends the Sentinel flying away from the mansion.<br /><br /> <br /><br /> <br /><br /> <br /><br /> Whilst Logan and the others finish off the Sentinel, Kitty and the students discover the body of Wing. They try to leave but the exit is gone. As Kitty is about to leave to get help the dead body of Wing re-animates and begins taunting and threatening the students.<br /><br /> <br /><br /> <br /><br /> <br /><br /> Emma arrives with Hank&rsquo;s help as the X-Men fail to gain access to the Danger Room, she tells them that the enemy is not IN the Danger Room but that it IS the Danger Room.<br /><br /> <br /><br /></p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, 737699300, 'Array', 0, '', 'published', '2012-06-16 13:10:00'),
(139, 14, 2006, 4, 26, 8, '1370117485.jpg', '<p>Scott finds himself replaying a memory from his past where he was with Jean and happy. A time when she was able to hold back his power so he could remove his visor.<br /><br /> <br /><br /> Scott is disgusted by Emma''s games. Emma taunts him about how much she wished Jean was around and their own psychic affair. Emma kisses him but when he catches a glance in the mirror he sees she is projecting hm as Logan. She again taunts him, this time that Logan is what he wanted to be, the love of her life.<br /><br /> <br /><br /> Meanwhile Kitty falls through the ceiling of the Mansion tv room naked due to being distracted by her ''activities'' with Piotr.<br /><br /> <br /><br /> Emma proceeds to the taunt Scott about why Xavier picked him as the leader of the X-Men.<br /><br /> <br /><br /> On the SWORD base, Brand is informed that the pre-cogs have determined who the Destroyer of Breakworld is.<br /><br /> <br /><br /> Emma takes Scott into his mind to ''The Bug Room''. She appears to force him to relive various bad memories.<br /><br /> <br /><br /> Hank is in his lab when he thinks Emma has come to see him, but when he gets a look he is shocked to see Cassandra Nova.<br /><br /> <br /><br /> Emma leaves Scott catatonic and his powers switched off.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, 100002077828287, 'Array', 0, '', 'published', '2012-06-16 13:11:00'),
(138, 13, 2006, 2, 22, 8, '1370117116.jpg', '<p>Emma is seen talking with Cassandra Nova prior to the devastation of Genosha, she tells her how millions will die and Emma will survive because she is going to give her a secondary mutation. She taunts Emma saying she is out of her league and couldn''t stop her.<br /><br /><br /> <br /><br /><br /> Logan has the students in the repaired yet inactive Danger Room and warns them that despite the fact that many students are gone due to M-Day, they are there to learn combat.<br /><br /><br /> <br /><br /><br /> Whilst napping with Piotr outside under a tree, Kitty has a nightmare about her father coming back and blaming her for letting them all die on Genosha.<br /><br /><br /> <br /><br /><br /> Emma appears to have caused the nightmare as she watches from the Mansion surrounded by the Hellfire Club.<br /><br /><br /> <br /><br /><br /> Although they all crave action Sebastian Shaw defers to the person he claims brought Hellfire back together: Perfection.<br /><br /><br /> <br /><br /><br /> Perfection assigns Emma to perform first.<br /><br /><br /> <br /><br /><br /> On the Hellicarrier Agent Brand and Agent Hill squabble over Brand''s disregard for the laws of Earth. Brand isn''t phased and warns her not to get in her way.<br /><br /><br /> <br /><br /><br /> Kitty goes to talk to Piotr in his room but finds she can''t. Piotr decides to take action and kisses her.<br /><br /><br /> <br /><br /><br /> Outside their door Emma walks away to her''s and Scott''s room. She attempts to seduce him by wearing Jean Grey''s form.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, 100002077828287, 'Array', 0, '', 'published', '2012-06-16 13:12:00'),
(137, 12, 2005, 8, 31, 8, '1370117078.jpg', '<p>As the massive monster of sentinel powers up it''s main weapons Kitty orders them to grab her and she phases them causing the beam to leave them unharmed.<br /><br /><br /> <br /><br /><br /> With insufficient power for a second blast it sends out a swarm of smaller robots that keep the X-Men busy as Beast attempts to remove Professor X from the battlefield. Danger rebuilds herself and chases after them, but Hank gives into his instincts which makes it harder for her to predict his moves.<br /><br /><br /> <br /><br /><br /> During the fighting Emma leaves the battle to speak to the unknown voice that she has been hearing, it tells her that soon she could drop the facade.<br /><br /><br /> <br /><br /><br /> Emma returns to the battle and Kitty orders Colossus to throw her as he does Wolverine.<br /><br /><br /> <br /><br /><br /> Beast defeats Danger''s body leaving Xavier to deal with Beast''s ''beast''.<br /><br /><br /> <br /><br /><br /> Kitty finds herself stuck in a stalemate with the sentinel,if she phases through the circuits it will reroute, if she becomes solid it will shoot.<br /><br /><br /> <br /><br /><br /> Instead she tells it to access a memory file that Danger locked away from it.<br /><br /><br /> <br /><br /><br /> The file contains the memory of the genocide. Something it did when it was a mere machine with no sense of self. But now it is alive and it leaves Earth to deal with these memories and try to come to terms with it.<br /><br /><br /> <br /><br /><br /> Colossus confronts Xavier, Danger told Colossus when he held her head that Xavier knew when she first became alive. Xavier admits he was wrong but still expects the X-Men to forgive and trust him.<br /><br /><br /> <br /><br /><br /> They leave him on Genosha disillusioned with their trusted leader.<br /><br /><br /> <br /><br /><br /> As the X-Men leave the the voices Emma hears are revealed to be the Hellfire Club.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, 100002077828287, 'Array', 0, '', 'published', '2012-06-16 13:13:00'),
(129, 9, 2005, 3, 1, 8, '1370112701.jpg', '<p>Whilst the X-Men discuss the ramifications of the Danger Room gaining sentience Kitty mobilizes the students as they defend themselves against the Danger Room which is controlling Wing''s corpse like a puppet.<br /><br /><br /> <br /><br /><br /> The Room continues to taunt and torture them as it hi-jacks the Blackbird<br /><br /><br /> <br /><br /><br /> Whilst conversing with Kitty it reveals it''s history and how it learnt to become what it is today, a machine built to kill, but never permitted to kill thanks to the safety features on the Room.<br /><br /><br /> <br /><br /><br /> Eventually Kitty realises that the Room is trying to get the X-Men to free it''s command core but she is too late as the room has attained a cybernetic form with female design.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, 100002077828287, 'Array', 0, '', 'published', '2012-06-16 13:14:00'),
(135, 10, 2005, 5, 11, 8, '1370116958.jpg', '<p>The new Danger Room construct speeds towards the remains of Genosha and Professor Charles Xavier, all the while it communicates with the Professor talking and taunting about how it easily defeated his X-Men at first.<br /><br /><br /> <br /><br /><br /> Abigail Brand monitors the situation from her SWORD base in orbit.<br /><br /><br /> <br /><br /><br /> Kitty warns her team mates to abandon their training as Danger knows how they fight.<br /><br /><br /> <br /><br /><br /> Brand confronts Ord to see if it is one of his friends attacking the X-Men, but he denies it.<br /><br /><br /> <br /><br /><br /> The X-Men begin to rally against Danger but she uses knowledge beyond their fighting tactics to defeat them.<br /><br /><br /> <br /><br /><br /> Emma willingly allows herself to be taken out because Danger knows a secret about her.<br /><br /><br /> <br /><br /><br /> Danger explains that she needs fulfillment and to achieve it she needs to kill Xavier.<br /><br /><br /> <br /><br /><br /> Xavier warns Danger that although she has fought the X-Men, he has never fought him.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, 100002077828287, 'Array', 0, '', 'published', '2012-06-16 13:15:00'),
(136, 11, 2005, 9, 7, 8, '1370117016.jpg', '<p>Danger lands on Genosha expecting to find the Professor an easy kill, but he tricks and uses a truck to drive her into a nearby power station. He implies that Magneto or another magnetic mutant has killed all other electronics in the area for him.<br /><br /><br /> <br /><br /><br /> Meanwhile, Elixir heals the X-Men and Kitty figures out where Danger has gone. They contact the Avengers and Fantastic four for a lift to Genosha.<br /><br /><br /> <br /><br /><br /> Xavier uses his victory over Danger to drag her into his mind to talk, she attempts to restore her body but Xavier has chopped it up and carries her head as he drags himself along.<br /><br /><br /> <br /><br /><br /> The X-Men arrive in a borrowed jet from the Fantastic Four and parachute down so that Danger can''t control it.<br /><br /><br /> <br /><br /><br /> The X-Men are too late as Danger reactivates the remnants of the Sentinel monster that eradicated Genosha.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, 100002077828287, 'Array', 0, '', 'published', '2012-06-16 13:16:00'),
(141, 15, 2006, 6, 21, 8, '1370117514.jpg', '<p>Emma arrives at the kitchen having forced herself to produce fake tears. She acts distraught as she explains Scott''s condition and Piotr, Kitty and Logan immediately get to work.<br /><br /><br /> <br /><br /><br /> Cassandra Nova strips away Hank McCoy leaving nothing but the Beast, she does not seem to notice Logan behind her as he came to get Hank to help with Scott.<br /><br /><br /> <br /><br /><br /> Kitty leaves Piotr with Scott to search for intruders in the house but she unwittingly stumbles across a goth like woman who is part of Hellfire.<br /><br /><br /> <br /><br /><br /> Sebastian Shaw confronts Piotr in the infirmary. Piotr transforms and immediately starts beating Shaw.<br /><br /><br /> <br /><br /><br /> The goth lady causes Kitty to fall through the ground as she loses control of her powers.<br /><br /><br /> <br /><br /><br /> Wolverine has been turned into a little boy, a spoilt little boy from the 19th century. He makes paper-doll chains until he sees the now feral Beast and then runs in terror.<br /><br /><br /> <br /><br /><br /> Kitty continues to phase deeper into the earth with no control.<br /><br /><br /> <br /><br /><br /> Hisako tries to comfort Blindfold who is hiding in the toilets but Logan bursts in with Beast on his tail. Logan hides behind Hisako leaving her to deal with the feral mutant.<br /><br /><br /> <br /><br /><br /> Agent Brand continues monitor the situation but Danger has boarded and secretly looks to strike a deal with Ord.<br /><br /><br /> <br /><br /><br /> Shaw eventually points out that Colossus has been feeding his power, he disables the metal mutant with a single shot.<br /><br /><br /> <br /><br /><br /> Hellfire reconvenes to report on their missions and all are dealt with and they are now ready to deal with the ''Main Event''.<br /><br /><br /> <br /><br /><br /> Kitty finally stops phasing and turns back prepared to fight Emma and stop her.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, 100002077828287, 'Array', 0, '', 'published', '2012-06-16 13:17:00'),
(142, 16, 2006, 8, 23, 8, '1370117970.jpg', '<p>Ord escapes SWORD custody with help from Danger.<br /><br /><br /> <br /><br /><br /> Logan is still running and hiding from the feral Hank whilst Hisako and Blindfold help each other to the infirmary. When they arrive Kitty emerges from the floor having managed to phase back up.<br /><br /><br /> <br /><br /><br /> In the depths of the subterranean levels the Hellfire Club have reached their destination. A box of some kind. Emma switches to her diamond form and hits it but lasers shoot out and throw her back. They seem unable to open it but it is implied that Kitty can get into it.<br /><br /><br /> <br /><br /><br /> Kitty manages to get the drop on Emma when she appears to be alone. She drags Emma into the walls and holds her phased in the rock so she can''t control her without killing herself.<br /><br /><br /> <br /><br /><br /> Emma states that she is working with four members of Hellfire, she withholds information about Perfection.<br /><br /><br /> <br /><br /><br /> Emma is found by Logan just as Perfection arrives, she removes her cloak and reveals herself to be The White Queen. This definitely causes confusion for Kitty.<br /><br /><br /> <br /><br /><br /> SWORD shoots down Ord and Danger''s shuttle but they aren''t on board, they track him down and Brand reveals that Colossus is the one destined to destroy Breakworld.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, 100002077828287, 'Array', 0, '', 'published', '2012-06-16 13:18:00'),
(143, 17, 2006, 9, 20, 8, '1370118003.jpg', '<p>Kitty hallucinates that she and Piotr have a son, Michael. But as he learns to walk and talk Xavier approaches and he along with Piotr and the rest of the X-Men turn on her and take her son away.<br /><br /><br /> <br /><br /><br /> Time passes in the hallucination and Kitty has been locked away from Michael for eighteen months. She threatens to kill Piotr unless he tells her where he son is.<br /><br /><br /> <br /><br /><br /> He tells her he is in the basement in a box.<br /><br /><br /> <br /><br /><br /> In the real world Kitty heads to the box the Hellfire Club want into.<br /><br /><br /> <br /><br /><br /> On the SWORD base Brand and her people have determined that Frost is behind the events at the Mansion. But also that there are traces of Cassandra Nova involved.<br /><br /><br /> <br /><br /><br /> They get a visual on Ord and Danger heading for the Manison from their mole in the X-Men. The mole wants to engage but Brand talks him down. The mole is Lockheed.<br /><br /><br /> <br /><br /><br /> As Kitty reaches the box Hisako and Blindfold try to reach the other X-Men.<br /><br /><br /> <br /><br /><br /> Kitty breaches the box as Danger and Ord arrive knocking out Hisako and Logan. Logan is brought to his natural state of mind by a can of beer that fell from the fridge.<br /><br /><br /> <br /><br /><br /> Piotr reaches Kitty as she retrieves the contents of the box which she believes is her son. In reality it is a slimy pulsating slug like mess.<br /><br /><br /> <br /><br /><br /> Both Piotr and Kitty collapse under the assault of Emma and Cassandra.<br /><br /><br /> <br /><br /><br /> The mess of slime turns out to be Cassandra Nova in some form but she intends to take over Emma Frosts body which all members of Hellfire and Emma herself seem to be eager to see. <br /><br /><br /> <br /><br /><br /> Emma is shot from behind and is shocked to see that Scott is there with a gun and his powers still deactivated.<br /><br /><br /></p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, 737699300, 'Array', 0, '', 'published', '2012-06-20 06:10:29'),
(144, 18, 2006, 11, 15, 8, '1370118030.jpg', '<p>Scott leans over Emma who he has just shot as Kitty and Piotr lie unconscious nearby with the slimy mess from the box. Cassandra Nova comes up behind him to attack but he spins around and shoots her in the head.<br /><br /><br /> <br /><br /><br /> He communicates telepathically with Blindfold who is providing him with psychic protection from Emma and the Hellfire Club. But Blindfold warns him that she is about to distracted by a feral Beast.<br /><br /><br /> <br /><br /><br /> Beast doesn''t seem to interested in her having recently eaten but Blindfold knows she has to deal with him. She has a box which belongs to Hank McCoy which will help subdue him. In it is a ball of red string.<br /><br /><br /> <br /><br /><br /> Ord and Danger continue to smash through the house search for the X-Men.<br /><br /><br /> <br /><br /><br /> Piotr wakes up to find Scott shooting the rest of the Hellfire Club, but Scott claims he isn''t shooting them as he is an X-Man. He is making a point.<br /><br /><br /> <br /><br /><br /> Danger and Ord are interrupted when Hisako attacks them, she keeps it up until Logan arrives and joins her.<br /><br /><br /> <br /><br /><br /> Kitty awakens and Scott tells her she has to find and save Emma.<br /><br /><br /> <br /><br /><br /> Danger uses Logan against Hisako but Hank arrives and saves them by using a unique magnetic field that sticks them to the ceiling without affecting Logan. Together they help patch up Hisako.<br /><br /><br /> <br /><br /><br /> After Kitty rescues Emma, Scott explains to the other X-Men that the Hellfire Club wasn''t really there. It was all Emma under Cassandra Nova''s influence as she had hidden certain suggestions in Emma''s brain.<br /><br /><br /> <br /><br /><br /> Danger builds a non-metallic body to free herself and Ord.<br /><br /><br /> <br /><br /><br /> Cassandra tries to get Emma to put her in Hisako.<br /><br /><br /> <br /><br /><br /> Kitty wants to kill Emma for what she put her through but Scott explains that Cassandra brought her here to open the box, Emma brought so she would kill her if this occurred. A failsafe.<br /><br /><br /> <br /><br /><br /> Just as Scott explains to Emma that she has a choice, that she can put Cassandra back, Ord and Danger break in but Agent Brand teleports them up to her ship and flies off leaving the students at the Mansion alone.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, 737699300, 'Array', 0, '', 'published', '2012-06-20 15:14:07'),
(166, 9, 1964, 10, 10, 1, '1367881067.jpg', '<p>As Captain America struggles with hallucinations of Baron Zemo, Zemo and his Masters of Evil are trapped between the sixth and seventh dimensions, there tempers are thin and they are only able to escape through the Enchantresses magic.<br /><br /> <br /><br /> They return to Zemo''s jungle kingdom in the Amazon where they hatch their plan. They return to New York where they pay the bail of Simon Williams, a millionaire arrested for embezzlement and blames Tony Stark for his downfall.<br /><br /> <br /><br /> Zemo bombards Williams with potent Ionic rays that give him super strength and invulnerability. They give him a costume and name him ''Wonder Man''. After testing his abilities they send him to New York to join the Avengers as a spy. But they warn him that the ionic rays will kill him without the antidote that Zemo has, keeping him loyal to him.<br /><br /> <br /><br /> Zemo, Executioner and Enchantress rob a bank allowing the Avengers to see Wonder Man drive them off.<br /><br /> <br /><br /> The Avengers are at first eager to accept Wonder Man but when he tells them he was captured by Zemo and experimented on Captain America refuses to believe Zemo would let him escape and suspects a plot. The Enchantress intervenes and makes them believe Wonder Man is dying and needs their help.<br /><br /> <br /><br /> The Avengers each begin to work on their cures for Wonder Man but he kidnaps the Wasp without them knowing and takes her to the Amazon. Zemo then makes him call the Avengers for help but only Iron Man is immediately available and he heads off to help whilst the others follow.<br /><br /> <br /><br /> The Avengers are beaten by Zemo the Masters of Evil and Wonder Man but when Zemo goes to kill them Wonder Man objects and saves them driving off the Masters of Evil.<br /><br /> <br /><br /> Without the antidote Wonder Man dies but earns some respect from the Avengers.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, 737699300, 'Array', 0, '', 'published', '2013-05-06 15:57:47'),
(160, 8, 1964, 9, 10, 1, '1367512212.jpg', 'The Avengers are called to their Headquarters at Tony Stark''s mansion where they are given a secure connection to the Pentagon.  There they see an amateur video of a UFO landing in Virginia.<br /><br />\r\n<br /><br />\r\nThe alien within calls himself Kang the Conqueror and he destroys the US Army''s weapons and orders the world leaders come and listen to his demands.<br /><br />\r\n<br /><br />\r\nThe Avengers immediately jet off to Virginia to deal with Kang.<br /><br />\r\n<br /><br />\r\nKang easily able to outmatch all of the Avengers and captures them all except The Wasp who escapes and joins up with Rick Jones and the Teen Brigade.<br /><br />\r\n<br /><br />\r\nThe Wasp heads back to Headquarters to find a weapon in the labs to use against Kang whilst Rick Jones and the Teen Brigade sneak past the Army to trick Kang into thinking they want to help him.<br /><br />\r\n<br /><br />\r\nThey manage to free the Avengers and sabotage some equipment until the Wasp returns with a weapon.  They successfully manage to drive Kang off of the planet.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 737699300, NULL, 0, '', 'published', '2013-05-02 09:30:12'),
(167, 10, 1964, 11, 10, 1, '1371589307.jpg', '<p>After a training session the Avengers hold a meeting where Iron Man raises the issue of officially making Rick Jones an Avenger due to his previous actions. &nbsp;Captain America objects as he believes it is his decision.</p>\r\n<p>Rick Jones overhears and questions the Captain but Captain America asks for his trust as he still bears the guilt for Bucky.</p>\r\n<p>Meanwhile Zemo, The Executioner and The Enchantress are planning their next move in the Amazon when they are confronted by Immortus. &nbsp;He challenges the Masters of Evil in a bid to join them. &nbsp;He proves his power by calling Paul Bunyan of legends to defeat the Executioner but the Executioner prevails. &nbsp;Zemo challenges Immortus to defeat the Avengers and prove his loyalty.</p>\r\n<p>Rick Jones and the Teen Brigade see an advert in the newspaper claiming they can get super powers. &nbsp;Rick Jones goes to visit the person at the address and finds Immortus who tells him the Ad was placed to bring Rick to him. &nbsp;Immortus calls in Atilla the Hun to capture Rick Jones who puts up a good fight but is quickly subdued.</p>\r\n<p>Captain America finds Rick missing and the Teen Brigade tell him about the ad. &nbsp;He rushes to the address in the paper where Immortus tells him that the Avengers told him that capturing Rick Jones was the best way to control the Captain. &nbsp;He returns to the Avengers and confronts them, he is enraged and attacks the Avengers who try to subdue him. &nbsp;They eventually get Captain America to calm down even though he no longer trusts them and they go to Immortus.</p>\r\n<p>Immortus pits each of the Avengers against a character from history:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Ant man &amp; The Wasp vs. Goliath</li>\r\n<li>Iron Man vs. Merlin</li>\r\n<li>Thor vs. Hercules</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Captain America, meanwhile, fights through a medieval army as Immortus promises to return Rick to him if he wins. &nbsp;The Avengers return home believing Captain America is gone but they are attacked by The Masters of Evil. &nbsp;They are saved by Captain America who defeated Immortus'' army and was returned home with Rick.</p>\r\n<p>Seeing their defeat the Enchantress turns back time to before Immortus arrived.</p>\r\n<p>The Avengers don''t remember the events but the Masters of Evil do. &nbsp;This time they avoid Immortus.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, 737699300, NULL, 0, '', 'published', '2013-06-18 14:01:47');
